{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775859143365,"sessionID":"ses_2868ce86affePxqVbkjfhLn59M","part":{"id":"prt_d79740ec30013k0IaSiuJAMKD5","messageID":"msg_d797404e2001A93kIkF94NdFi4","sessionID":"ses_2868ce86affePxqVbkjfhLn59M","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_7322862c4fca4a44ba8a9a1a","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/proposal.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/proposal.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-024: DockerService 封装\n2: \n3: ## Purpose\n4: \n5: 为 AgentCube Python CLI 封装 Docker SDK 交互层，提供镜像构建、推送、查询、删除等核心能力的统一服务接口。\n6: \n7: 当前 BuildRuntime 和 PublishRuntime 需要与 Docker 引擎交互完成镜像生命周期管理，但缺乏统一的服务层封装。本 AR 在 `agentcube/services/docker_service.py` 中实现 `DockerService` 类，将 Docker SDK 调用抽象为可测试、可复用的服务方法。\n8: \n9: ## Scope\n10: \n11: ### In Scope\n12: \n13: 1. **`DockerService` 类实现**\n14:    - `check_docker_available()` — 验证 Docker 守护进程可用\n15:    - `build_image()` — 构建 Docker 镜像并打标\n16:    - `get_image_info()` / `_get_image_info()` — 查询本地镜像元数据\n17:    - `_format_size()` — 格式化字节大小为可读字符串\n18:    - `push_image()` — 推送镜像到 registry（支持登录、重新打标）\n19:    - `_docker_login_sdk()` — Docker registry 认证\n20:    - `_tag_image_sdk()` — 镜像重新打标\n21:    - `remove_image()` — 删除本地镜像\n22: \n23: 2. **服务集成**\n24:    - 更新 `agentcube/services/__init__.py` 导出 `DockerService`\n25:    - BuildRuntime 通过 DockerService 构建镜像\n26:    - PublishRuntime 通过 DockerService 推送镜像\n27: \n28: 3. **错误处理**\n29:    - Docker 不可用 → `RuntimeError(\"Docker is not available or not running\")`\n30:    - SDK 异常 → 包装为有意义的错误信息向上抛出\n31:    - 认证失败 → 明确提示凭证问题\n32: \n33: ### Out of Scope\n34: \n35: - Docker Compose 支持\n36: - 多阶段构建优化\n37: - 镜像扫描/安全检测\n38: - 远程 Docker 主机连接（仅支持本地 Docker socket）\n39: - Go CLI 或其他语言 SDK 的 Docker 封装\n40: \n41: ## Impact Analysis\n42: \n43: ### Dependencies\n44: \n45: | 依赖 | 用途 | 影响 |\n46: |------|------|------|\n47: | `docker>=6.0.0` | Docker SDK for Python | 已有依赖，无新增 |\n48: | `rich>=13.0.0` | 可选进度显示 | 已有依赖，无新增 |\n49: \n50: ### Affected Components\n51: \n52: - **`agentcube/services/docker_service.py`**（新增）：`DockerService` 类实现\n53: - **`agentcube/services/__init__.py`**（修改）：导出 `DockerService`\n54: - **`agentcube/runtime/build_runtime.py`**（修改）：调用 `DockerService.build_image()`\n55: - **`agentcube/runtime/publish_runtime.py`**（修改）：调用 `DockerService.push_image()`\n56: \n57: ### 与现有组件的交互\n58: \n59: | 组件 | 交互方式 | 影响 |\n60: |------|----------|------|\n61: | `BuildRuntime` | 实例化 `DockerService` 调用 `build_image()` | 替换内联 Docker SDK 调用 |\n62: | `PublishRuntime` | 实例化 `DockerService` 调用 `push_image()` | 统一推送流程 |\n63: | `docker.DockerClient` | 通过 `docker.from_env()` 获取 | 封装 SDK 细节 |\n64: \n65: ### Risk Assessment\n66: \n67: | 风险 | 等级 | 缓解措施 |\n68: |------|------|----------|\n69: | Docker SDK 版本兼容性 | 低 | 锁定 `docker>=6.0.0`，测试覆盖最小版本 |\n70: | 凭证泄露 | 中 | 密码仅内存传递，不写入日志或文件 |\n71: | 构建超时 | 低 | 调用方可设置超时参数，DockerService 记录构建时间 |\n72: | Docker 守护进程未运行 | 中 | `check_docker_available()` 前置检查，友好错误提示 |\n73: \n74: ## Alternatives Considered\n75: \n76: ### 1. 直接在 Runtime 中调用 Docker SDK（❌ 不采用）\n77: \n78: **做法**：BuildRuntime/PublishRuntime 直接使用 `docker.from_env()` 和内联逻辑。\n79: \n80: **优点**：减少一层封装，代码更直接  \n81: **缺点**：\n82: - Docker SDK 调用散落在多个 Runtime 类中，难以维护\n83: - 重复实现登录、打标、错误处理等逻辑\n84: - 单元测试需要 mock Docker SDK 多处调用点\n85: - 违反单一职责原则\n86: \n87: **决策**：不采用。现有 spec 已明确定义 `DockerService` 接口，应保持服务层抽象。\n88: \n89: ### 2. 使用 subprocess 调用 docker CLI（❌ 不采用）\n90: \n91: **做法**：通过 `subprocess.run([\"docker\", \"build\", ...])` 执行 Docker 命令。\n92: \n93: **优点**：不依赖 Docker SDK Python 包  \n94: **缺点**：\n95: - 需要解析 CLI 输出文本，脆弱且难以获取结构化信息\n96: - 无法利用 SDK 的流式日志、错误码等特性\n97: - 跨平台兼容性差（Windows Docker Desktop 路径问题）\n98: - 已有 `docker>=6.0.0` 依赖，无需引入新方案\n99: \n100: **决策**：不采用。Docker SDK 提供更稳定、类型安全的 API。\n101: \n102: ### 3. 统一服务层封装（✅ 选定方案）\n103: \n104: **做法**：实现 `DockerService` 类，封装所有 Docker SDK 交互。\n105: \n106: **优点**：\n107: - 与现有 `MetadataService`、`KubernetesProvider`、`AgentCubeProvider` 架构一致\n108: - 单一职责，便于单元测试（mock 一个服务类）\n109: - 复用登录、打标、查询等逻辑\n110: - 错误处理集中化\n111: \n112: **缺点**：\n113: - 增加一层间接调用\n114: - 需要维护服务接口与 Runtime 调用的契约\n115: \n116: **决策**：采用。符合项目现有架构模式，spec 已明确定义接口。\n117: \n118: ## Implementation Notes\n119: \n120: ### DockerService 类实现\n121: \n122: ```python\n123: class DockerService:\n124:     def __init__(self, verbose: bool = False) -> None:\n125:         self.verbose = verbose\n126:         self.client = docker.from_env()\n127: \n128:     def check_docker_available(self) -> bool:\n129:         try:\n130:             self.client.ping()\n131:             return True\n132:         except docker.errors.DockerException:\n133:             return False\n134: \n135:     def build_image(\n136:         self,\n137:         dockerfile_path: Path,\n138:         context_path: Path,\n139:         image_name: str,\n140:         tag: str = \"latest\",\n141:         build_args: Optional[Dict[str, str]] = None,\n142:     ) -> Dict[str, str]:\n143:         # 调用 client.images.build()\n144:         # 支持 buildargs 传入代理配置\n145:         # 返回 {image_name, image_id, image_size, build_time}\n146: \n147:     def get_image_info(self, image_name: str) -> Dict[str, str]:\n148:         # 公共入口，可添加缓存\n149:         return self._get_image_info(image_name)\n150: \n151:     def _get_image_info(self, image_name: str) -> Dict[str, str]:\n152:         # 直接调用 SDK 查询镜像属性\n153:         # 返回 ID、大小、创建时间等\n154: \n155:     def _format_size(self, size_bytes: int) -> str:\n156:         # 转换为 KB/MB/GB 可读格式\n157: \n158:     def push_image(\n159:         self,\n160:         image_name: str,\n161:         registry_url: Optional[str] = None,\n162:         username: Optional[str] = None,\n163:         password: Optional[str] = None,\n164:     ) -> Dict[str, str]:\n165:         # 若提供凭证，先登录\n166:         # 若指定 registry_url，重新打标\n167:         # 流式推送，返回 {pushed_image, push_time}\n168: \n169:     def _docker_login_sdk(self, registry: Optional[str], username: str, password: str) -> None:\n170:         # 调用 client.login()\n171: \n172:     def _tag_image_sdk(self, source_image: str, target_image: str) -> None:\n173:         # 调用 image.tag()\n174: \n175:     def remove_image(self, image_name: str) -> bool:\n176:         # 调用 client.images.remove()\n177:         # 成功返回 True，失败记录警告返回 False\n178: ```\n179: \n180: ### 与 BuildRuntime 集成\n181: \n182: ```python\n183: # BuildRuntime._build_local() 中：\n184: docker_service = DockerService(verbose=self.verbose)\n185: if not docker_service.check_docker_available():\n186:     raise RuntimeError(\"Docker is not available or not running\")\n187: \n188: build_result = docker_service.build_image(\n189:     dockerfile_path=workspace_path / \"Dockerfile\",\n190:     context_path=workspace_path,\n191:     image_name=metadata.image[\"name\"],\n192:     tag=tag,\n193:     build_args={\"HTTP_PROXY\": proxy} if proxy else None,\n194: )\n195: ```\n196: \n197: ### 与 PublishRuntime 集成\n198: \n199: ```python\n200: # PublishRuntime._prepare_local_image() 中：\n201: docker_service = DockerService(verbose=self.verbose)\n202: docker_service.push_image(\n203:     image_name=metadata.image[\"name\"],\n204:     registry_url=options.get(\"registry_url\"),\n205:     username=options.get(\"registry_username\"),\n206:     password=options.get(\"registry_password\"),\n207: )\n208: ```\n209: \n210: ### 测试策略\n211: \n212: - **单元测试**：mock `docker.DockerClient` 验证各方法行为\n213:   - `check_docker_available()` — ping 成功/失败\n214:   - `build_image()` — 正常构建、buildargs 传递、异常处理\n215:   - `push_image()` — 登录+推送、仅推送、registry 重新打标\n216:   - `remove_image()` — 成功删除、删除失败返回 False\n217: - **集成测试**：在 Docker 可用环境下验证完整构建/推送流程（可选）\n218: - **异常测试**：Docker 不可用、认证失败、镜像不存在、构建失败等场景\n219: \n220: ## Acceptance Criteria\n221: \n222: 1. **DockerService 类**\n223:    - [ ] `check_docker_available()` 正确检测 Docker 守护进程状态\n224:    - [ ] `build_image()` 成功构建镜像并返回完整信息字典\n225:    - [ ] `build_image()` 支持 `build_args` 传递代理配置\n226:    - [ ] `get_image_info()` 返回镜像 ID、大小、创建时间\n227:    - [ ] `_format_size()` 正确格式化字节为 KB/MB/GB\n228:    - [ ] `push_image()` 支持无 registry 本地推送\n229:    - [ ] `push_image()` 支持 registry 登录+重新打标+推送\n230:    - [ ] `push_image()` 流式日志输出（verbose 模式）\n231:    - [ ] `_docker_login_sdk()` 认证成功/失败处理\n232:    - [ ] `_tag_image_sdk()` 正确打标\n233:    - [ ] `remove_image()` 成功返回 True，失败返回 False 并记录警告\n234: \n235: 2. **错误处理**\n236:    - [ ] Docker 不可用抛出 `RuntimeError(\"Docker is not available or not running\")`\n237:    - [ ] 认证失败抛出有意义的错误信息\n238:    - [ ] 镜像不存在时抛出明确异常\n239:    - [ ] 构建失败时异常信息包含构建日志\n240: \n241: 3. **集成**\n242:    - [ ] `agentcube/services/__init__.py` 导出 `DockerService`\n243:    - [ ] BuildRuntime 使用 `DockerService.build_image()` 替代内联调用\n244:    - [ ] PublishRuntime 使用 `DockerService.push_image()` 替代内联调用\n245:    - [ ] 与现有 `MetadataService`、`KubernetesProvider` 风格一致\n246: \n247: 4. **代码质量**\n248:    - [ ] 完整类型注解\n249:    - [ ] 所有公开方法有 docstring\n250:    - [ ] 通过现有 lint/typecheck\n251:    - [ ] 单元测试覆盖率 ≥ 80%\n252: \n253: ## Status\n254: \n255: - [ ] 提案审查\n256: - [ ] 实现\n257: - [ ] 验证\n\n(End of file - total 257 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-024: DockerService 封装\n\n## Purpose\n\n为 AgentCube Python CLI 封装 Docker SDK 交互层，提供镜像构建、推送、查询、删除等核心能力的统一服务接口。\n\n当前 BuildRuntime 和 PublishRuntime 需要与 Docker 引擎交互完成镜像生命周期管理，但缺乏统一的服务层封装。本 AR 在 `agentcube/services/docker_service.py` 中实现 `DockerService` 类，将 Docker SDK 调用抽象为可测试、可复用的服务方法。\n\n## Scope\n\n### In Scope\n\n1. **`DockerService` 类实现**\n   - `check_docker_available()` — 验证 Docker 守护进程可用\n   - `build_image()` — 构建 Docker 镜像并打标\n   - `get_image_info()` / `_get_image_info()` — 查询本地镜像元数据\n   - `_format_size()` — 格式化字节大小为可读字符串\n   - `push_image()` — 推送镜像到 registry（支持登录、重新打标）\n   - `_docker_login_sdk()` — Docker registry 认证\n   - `_tag_image_sdk()` — 镜像重新打标","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/proposal.md","time":{"start":1775859143348,"end":1775859143362}}}}
